#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:13
msgid "Gradient"
msgstr "グラデーション"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:17
msgid "Gradient Fill"
msgstr "グラデーション塗りつぶし"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:21
msgid ""
"Fills the layer with a gradient in the same way as the gradient tool does."
msgstr ""
"グラデーションツールが行うのと同じ方法で、レイヤーをグラデーションで塗りつぶ"
"します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:24
msgid "General Options"
msgstr "一般的なオプション"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:28
msgid ""
"This will draw a straight gradient. The distance and angle between the start "
"and end points will define the size and rotation of the gradient, "
"respectively."
msgstr ""
"直線グラデーションを描きます。開始点と終了点の距離と角度はそれぞれグラデー"
"ションの大きさと方向になります。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:34
msgid "Linear"
msgstr "リニア"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:34
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:43
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:51
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:59
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:67
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:75
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:83
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:92
msgid "Left: **None**. Middle: **Forwards**. Right: **Alternating**."
msgstr "左: **なし**。中央: **順に繰り返し**。右: **反転して繰り返し**。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:37
msgid ""
"This will draw a straight gradient, mirrored along the axis. The distance "
"and angle between the start and end points will define the size and rotation "
"of the gradient, respectively."
msgstr ""
"軸で反転した直線グラデーションを描きます。開始点と終了点の距離と角度はそれぞ"
"れグラデーションの大きさと方向になります。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:43
msgid "Bilinear"
msgstr "バイリニア"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:46
msgid ""
"This will draw the gradient from a center, defined by the start point, with "
"a radius equal to the distance between the start and end points."
msgstr ""
"中心をグラデーションの開始点と定義し、終了点と半径の等しい距離にグラデーショ"
"ンを描きます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:51
msgid "Radial"
msgstr "放射状"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:54
msgid ""
"This will draw the gradient from a center in a square shape, defined by the "
"start point. The distance and angle between the start and end points will "
"define the distance from that center to a side of the square and its "
"rotation, respectively."
msgstr ""
"中心をグラデーションの開始点と定義し、四角の形に描きます。開始点と終了点の距"
"離と角度はそれぞれ四角の中心から辺の距離と方向に対応します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:59
msgid "Square"
msgstr "四角"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:62
msgid ""
"This will wrap the gradient around a center, defined by the start point. The "
"angle between the start and end points will define where the gradient starts."
msgstr ""
"中心を開始点と定義して、グラデーションを回転させます。開始点と終了点の角度は"
"グラデーションの開始場所に対応します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:67
msgid "Conical"
msgstr "円すい状"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:70
msgid ""
"This will wrap the gradient around a center, defined by the start point, but "
"will mirror the wrap once. The angle between the start and end points will "
"define where the gradient starts."
msgstr ""
"中心を開始点と定義して、グラデーションを回転させますが、一度反転させます。開"
"始点と終了点の角度はグラデーションの開始場所に対応します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:75
msgid "Conical-symmetric"
msgstr "円すい状(対称)"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:78
msgid ""
"This will draw the gradient spiral from a center, defined by the start "
"point. The distance and angle between the start and end points will define "
"the distance between loops and the rotation of the spiral, respectively."
msgstr ""
"中心をグラデーションの開始点と定義し、らせん状に描きます。開始点と終了点の距"
"離と角度はそれぞれらせんの繰り返し間隔と方向に対応します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:83
msgid "Spiral"
msgstr "らせん状"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:86
msgid ""
"This will draw the gradient spiral from a center, defined by the start "
"point, but direction is flipped perpendicular to the line that passes "
"through the star and end points. The distance and angle between the start "
"and end points will define the distance between loops and the rotation of "
"the spiral, respectively."
msgstr ""
"中心をグラデーションの開始点と定義し、らせん状に描きますが、開始点と終了点を"
"結ぶ線に対し90度曲げられます。開始点と終了点の距離と角度はそれぞれらせんの繰"
"り返し間隔と方向に対応します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:92
msgid "Reverse Spiral"
msgstr "らせん状(反転)"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:95
msgid "This will shape the gradient depending on the image bounds."
msgstr "画像の境界によってグラデーションの形を決めます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:97
msgid "Shape:"
msgstr "形状:"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:97
msgid "Shaped"
msgstr "図形内に限定"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:100
msgid "None"
msgstr "なし"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:101
msgid "This will extend the gradient into infinity."
msgstr "グラデーションを無限に伸ばします。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:102
msgid "Forward"
msgstr "順に繰り返し"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:103
msgid "This will repeat the gradient into one direction."
msgstr "グラデーションを1方向に繰り返します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:105
msgid "Repeat:"
msgstr "繰り返し:"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:105
msgid "Alternating"
msgstr "反転して繰り返し"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:105
msgid ""
"This will repeat the gradient, alternating the normal direction and the "
"reversed."
msgstr ""
"グラデーションを通常の方向と反対の方向に切り替えていきながら繰り返します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:108
msgid "Reverse"
msgstr "反転"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:108
msgid "Reverses the direction of the gradient."
msgstr "グラデーションの方向を反転させます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:111
msgid "Controls how smooth is the border between repetitions."
msgstr "繰り返し間の境界をどれだけスムーズにするかを決めます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:113
msgid "A value equal to 0 means there is no smoothing. The border is aliased."
msgstr "値を0にするとスムーズ化せず、境界線はエイリアスになります。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:114
msgid ""
"A value greater than 0 tells Krita how many pixels to each side of the "
"border should be smoothed."
msgstr "0より高い値は Krita はそのピクセル数で境界をスムーズ化します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:118
msgid "Antialias threshold"
msgstr "アンチエイリアスしきい値"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:118
msgid "Left: **0**. Middle: **0.5**. Right: **1**."
msgstr "左: **0**。中央: **0.5**。右: **1**。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:121
msgid "Positioning Options"
msgstr "位置オプション"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:124
msgid "Start"
msgstr "開始"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:124
msgid ""
"Allows you to set the start point for the gradient (in the gradient tool "
"this is the point where you first click)."
msgstr ""
"グラデーションの開始点を設定することができます(グラデーションツールでは最初に"
"クリックしたところになります)。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:127
msgid "End"
msgstr "終了"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:127
msgid ""
"Allows you to set the endpoint for the gradient (in the gradient tool this "
"is the point where you release the mouse button after dragging)."
msgstr ""
"グラデーションの終了点を設定することができます(グラデーションツールではドラッ"
"グした後にマウスボタンを離したところになります)。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:130
msgid ""
"You can make the values set for the start and end points mean different "
"things by changing the units associated with them:"
msgstr "開始点と終了点の値は紐づけられた単位を変更することができます:"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:132
msgid "Pixels"
msgstr "ピクセル"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:133
msgid "The value indicates a distance in pixels."
msgstr "ピクセルで表される距離です。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:135
msgid ""
"The value indicates a distance as a percentage of the width of the image. So "
"for example, if the image is 1000 pixels wide and 500 pixels high, and the "
"value is 25, then this would be translated to pixels as 250 (25% of the "
"width)."
msgstr ""
"百分率で表される画像幅の距離の値です。例えば、画像幅が1000ピクセルで高さが500"
"とし、値を25にするとピクセル数250(幅の25%)として解釈されます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:136
msgid "Percent of the width"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:139
msgid ""
"The value indicates a distance as a percentage of the height of the image. "
"So for example, if the image is 1000 pixels wide and 500 pixels high, and "
"the value is 25, then this would be translated to pixels as 125 (25% of the "
"height)."
msgstr ""
"百分率で表される画像高さの距離の値です。例えば、画像幅が1000ピクセルで高さが"
"500とし、値を25にするとピクセル数125(幅の25%)として解釈されます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:140
msgid "Percent of the height"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:143
msgid ""
"The value indicates a distance as a percentage of the shortest side of the "
"image. So for example, if the image is 1000 pixels wide and 500 pixels high, "
"and the value is 25, then this would be translated to pixels as 125 (25% of "
"the shortest side)."
msgstr ""
"画像の短い方の距離を百分率で表した値です。例えば、画像幅が1000ピクセルで高さ"
"が500とし、値を25にするとピクセル数125(短い方の25%)として解釈されます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:144
msgid "Percent of the shortest side"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:147
msgid ""
"The value indicates a distance as a percentage of the longest side of the "
"image. So for example, if the image is 1000 pixels wide and 500 pixels high, "
"and the value is 25, then this would be translated to pixels as 250 (25% of "
"the longest side)."
msgstr ""
"画像の長い方の距離を百分率で表した値です。例えば、画像幅が1000ピクセルで高さ"
"が500とし、値を25にするとピクセル数250(長い方の25%)として解釈されます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:149
msgid "Percent of the longest side"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:151
msgid ""
"Values that have percentage units are useful when changing the image size. "
"For example, if you want to have a linear gradient that always goes from the "
"left to the right of the image, you can set the start point to (x = 0 "
"pixels, y = 0 pixels) and the end point to (x = 100% of the width, y = 0 "
"pixels)."
msgstr ""
"百分率の値を持つ画像はサイズを変更するのにとても便利です。例えば、常に画像の"
"左から右へ走る直線グラデーションを作りたければ、開始点を(x = 0 ピクセル, y = "
"0 ピクセル) に、終了点を (x = 幅の 100%, y = 0 ピクセル)."

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:155
msgid ""
"On the other hand, if you want a gradient to have the same size regardless "
"of the image size, you should use pixel units."
msgstr ""
"言い換えると、画像にサイズに関わらずグラデーションを同じサイズに保つには、ピ"
"クセル単位を使います。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:159
msgid ""
"To make a gradient like the one in the image above, you can set the start "
"position's X coordinate to 80 pixels, 25% of the width, or 25% of the "
"longest side, and its Y coordinate to 60 pixels, 25% of the height, or 25% "
"of the shortest side. Likewise, you could set the end position's X "
"coordinate to 240 pixels, 75% of the width, or 75% of the longest side, and "
"its Y coordinate to 180 pixels, 75% of the height, or 75% of the shortest "
"side."
msgstr ""
"上の画像にあるようなグラデーションを作るには、開始点位置のX座標を80ピクセル"
"に、幅か長い方を25%、Y座標を60ピクセル、高さか短い方を25%に設定します。同じよ"
"うに終了点位置のX座標を240ピクセルに、幅か長い方を75%、Y座標を180ピクセル、高"
"さか短い方を75%に設定します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:166
msgid ""
"Keep in mind that if you use percentages the gradient's start and end "
"positions will adapt to the size of the image, while using pixel units will "
"make the gradient's positions be static."
msgstr ""
"グラデーションの開始終了位置に百分率を使うと画像のサイズに合わせて調節され、"
"ピクセル単位を使うと固定されることは留意しておいてください。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:167
msgid "Units"
msgstr "単位"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:170
msgid ""
"You can choose if the end point's coordinates are relative to the start "
"point."
msgstr "終了点の座標を開始点との相対位置にすることができます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:172
msgid "Absolute"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:173
msgid ""
"The end coordinate indicates a distance from the top-left corner of the "
"image."
msgstr "終了点の座標が画像左上からの距離になります。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:175
msgid "Positioning"
msgstr "位置"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:175
msgid "Relative"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:175
msgid "The end coordinate indicates a distance from the start point."
msgstr "終了点の座標が開始点からの距離になります。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:178
msgid "You can set the end point in cartesian or polar coordinates."
msgstr "終了点は直交または極座標系で設定できます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:181
msgid "Cartesian"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:181
msgid ""
"The coordinates of the end point are set by establishing horizontal and "
"vertical distances relative to the top-left corner of the image or to the "
"start point."
msgstr ""
"終了点の座標は画像左上か開始点との相対的な水平、垂直距離によって設定されま"
"す。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:184
msgid ""
"The coordinates of the end point are set by establishing an angle and a "
"distance relative to the start point."
msgstr "終了点の座標は開始点との相対的な距離と角度によって設定されます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:185
msgid "Polar"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:189
msgid ""
"To set the end point's position in the gradient on the image above, you "
"could use cartesian coordinates and set the X and Y coordinates relative to "
"the top-left corner of the image (absolute positioning) or relative to the "
"start point (relative positioning)."
msgstr ""
"上にある画像でグラデーション位置の終了点を設定するには、直交座標系を使い画像"
"左上(絶対座標)か開始点(相対座標)を基準にしたXとY座標を決めることができます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:193
msgid ""
"However, in some cases it is more convenient using polar coordinates and "
"setting the end point's position by establishing an angle and a distance "
"relative to the start point (polar coordinates are always relative to the "
"start point's position)."
msgstr ""
"しかし、極座標系を使って終了点を開始点との相対距離と角度で決める方が便利な場"
"合もあります(極座標系では常に開始点との相対位置になります)。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:195
msgid "Coordinate System"
msgstr "座標系"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:198
msgid "Gradient Colors"
msgstr "グラデーション色"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:200
msgid "Here you can select the actual colors used by the gradient."
msgstr "グラデーションで使う色はここで選択します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:-1
msgid "How to use Gradient generation in Krita."
msgstr "Krita グラデーション生成の使い方。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:0
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Gradient"
msgid "Linear Gradient."
msgstr "グラデーション"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:0
msgid ".. image:: /images/gradients/gradient_painter/linear.png"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:0
msgid ".. image:: /images/gradients/gradient_painter/bilinear.png"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:0
msgid ".. image:: /images/gradients/gradient_painter/radial.png"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:0
msgid ".. image:: /images/gradients/gradient_painter/square.png"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layer_generators/gradient.rst:0
msgid ".. image:: /images/gradients/gradient_painter/conical.png"
